Then decide which episode to use them in.

73
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:48,740
Right.

74
00:02:49,090 --> 00:02:51,215
Mainly, a lot of names were already used in season two.

75
00:02:51,215 --> 00:02:52,790
There was a family tree, remember?

76
00:02:52,790 --> 00:02:56,215
That family tree already included a lot of names.

77
00:02:56,215 --> 00:02:57,390
So it filled up a lot of spots.

78
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:58,390
And then,

79
