00:16:17,025 --> 00:16:18,700
We'd like to ask Dada a question.

450
00:16:18,700 --> 00:16:21,100
About our Ba Jie this season.

451
00:16:21,300 --> 00:16:24,100
First, could you help us summarize

452
00:16:24,100 --> 00:16:28,450
