453
00:16:28,950 --> 00:16:29,325
Sure.

454
00:16:29,325 --> 00:16:32,975
First of all, I think Ba Jie is a very dedicated person.

455
00:16:32,975 --> 00:16:36,050
She usually arrives in Changsha very late.

456
00:16:36,100 --> 00:16:39,400
But the next day, she still shows up in her best state for filming.

457
00:16:39,450 --> 00:16:40,550
She does her makeup in the morning.

458
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:42,850
She treats every role and look

459
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:45,750
and even when reviewing the character cards with her in the morning,

460
00:16:45,750 --> 00:16:47,525
she's always full of energy.

461
00:16:47,525 --> 00:16:48,750
She listens carefully when you explain the character cards.

462
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:49,000
And then,

463
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:51,900
she seriously communicates her understanding and feelings with you.

464
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,475
Most of the time, after finishing work,

465
00:16:53,475 --> 00:16:55,050
she still has to rush back to the film crew.

466
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,200
And then,

467
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:59,250
since filming in Dingnan isn't very convenient for transportation,

468
00:16:59,250 --> 00:17:01,475
after wrapping up, she goes straight back to the crew.

469
00:17:01,475 --> 00:17:03,425
So I really feel she's hardworking and dedicated.

470
00:17:03,425 --> 00:17:03,800
And also,

471
00:17:03,800 --> 00:17:05,050
secondly, in terms of styling,

472
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:06,450
Because I think

473
00:17:06,660 --> 00:17:08,160
she really is a miracle.

474
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:11,060
When we're designing the script,

475
00:17:11,060 --> 00:17:14,010
we think in advance about which looks will stand out.

476
00:17:14,260 --> 00:17:14,960
And then,

477
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:18,210
she always exceeds expectations with these looks.

478
00:17:18,210 --> 00:17:19,435
For this character's look,

479
00:17:19,435 --> 00:17:24,360
you imagine in your mind how it might turn out.

480
00:17:24,610 --> 00:17:26,660
But after the makeup is done,

481
00:17:26,740 --> 00:17:27,815
and she changes into the costume,

482
00:17:27,815 --> 00:17:30,515
she still surpasses your expectations.

483
00:17:30,515 --> 00:17:33,065
I remember the pirate time, I was waiting for her at the hotel entrance.

484
00:17:33,065 --> 00:17:34,015
She finished her makeup,

485
00:17:34,015 --> 00:17:35,590
and after she changed into the outfit and came out,

486
00:17:35,590 --> 00:17:38,090
she walked down the hallway looking so cool and confident.

487
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:38,865
At that moment,

488
00:17:38,865 --> 00:17:42,390
I felt like a real, vivid pirate leader appeared before me.

489
00:17:42,590 --> 00:17:42,915
Yeah.

490
00:17:42,915 --> 00:17:44,540
And the flower fairy outfit,

491
00:17:44,590 --> 00:17:44,990
she

492
00:17:45,260 --> 00:17:45,985
changed into it,

493
00:17:45,985 --> 00:17:47,560
and when she walked out of the room,

494
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:48,335
you couldn't help but marvel

495
00:17:48,335 --> 00:17:50,210
at how she could bring out such a unique feeling.

496
00:17:50,410 --> 00:17:52,860
You'd believe she really is a flower fairy in the human world.

497
00:17:52,860 --> 00:17:56,210
Especially when she held the bow and scattered flowers for that shot,

498
00:17:56,260 --> 00:17:58,660
you'd feel so grateful that she's part of this show.

499
00:17:59,010 --> 00:18:02,260
And every time, she actually takes her styling very seriously.

500
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:02,825
Oh.

501
00:18:02,825 --> 00:18:07,000
Everyone can see that in every episode, Ba Jie has a different little handbag.

502
00:18:07,150 --> 00:18:10,850
She carefully selects and matches all of them herself.

503
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:16,500
And I also remember, at the end, at the Good House,

504
00:18:16,500 --> 00:18:18,575
the red outfit she wore for the ceremony,

505
00:18:18,575 --> 00:18:20,050
she was carrying a small black bag.

506
00:18:20,050 --> 00:18:20,375
Right.

507
00:18:20,375 --> 00:18:22,400
And her dress was really long.

508
00:18:22,650 --> 00:18:24,950
And it was raining at the time.

509
00:18:24,950 --> 00:18:25,450
So then,

510
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:28,575
the dress dragged on the ground and got wet.

511
00:18:28,575 --> 00:18:31,700
At that time, to avoid delaying the filming schedule,

512
00:18:31,700 --> 00:18:35,075
