513
00:18:35,075 --> 00:18:36,350
She just grabbed a pair of scissors herself.

514
00:18:36,350 --> 00:18:37,375
And cut the dress short right away.

515
00:18:37,375 --> 00:18:39,850
So I think she's also someone who doesn't sweat the small stuff.

516
00:18:42,150 --> 00:18:43,450
You mentioned she has a lot of bags.

517
00:18:43,450 --> 00:18:44,400
The netizens are also very curious.

518
00:18:44,450 --> 00:18:46,600
They want to know what's inside her bags.

