00:18:50,990 --> 00:18:52,440
Basically, it's all snacks.

521
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:54,365
Just like Teacher Jingjing said,

522
00:18:54,365 --> 00:18:56,140
her bag is basically a snack

523
00:18:56,390 --> 00:18:57,440
supply station.

524
00:18:57,590 --> 00:18:57,990
Mm-hmm.

525
00:18:57,990 --> 00:18:59,640
There are lots of candies inside.

526
00:18:59,690 --> 00:19:01,440
For example, fruit candies and milk candies.

527
00:19:01,790 --> 00:19:04,390
And also the chocolate candies she likes.

528
00:19:04,790 --> 00:19:05,190
Yeah.

529
00:19:05,390 --> 00:19:06,465
There's also beef jerky,

530
00:19:06,465 --> 00:19:07,190
milk tablets,

531
00:19:07,520 --> 00:19:07,670
and then

532
00:19:07,670 --> 00:19:11,070
I remember once, when we were filming at the Pirate Mansion,

